{"tid":406160,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"係網上賣野遇到中、小學生真係世界級","createTime":"2017-09-19T12:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T10:53:34.000Z","uid":88343,"like":4,"dislike":165,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d8453ae573bf9b510481cdbd0960f00b05c1c6","tid":406160,"uid":88343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:11:35.000Z","msg":"暫時最有印象嘅有幾個：<br />\n<br />\n1:<br />\n有個同我住同區，但冇個日子夾到咁濟，佢話用順豐（呢吓我已經黑人問號），我話住咁近用郵寄、順豐好無謂。最後佢係銀行用機入數（佢冇銀行戶口，我仲要找錢比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），貨同找續就用密實袋裝住然後放入佢信箱，點知佢信箱又唔夠大放唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我打比佢問佢係邊，我睇吓可以係邊度等或者去搵佢，跟住佢話佢係附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有同呢個賣家傾吓計，佢中學生嚟，我同佢都係住新界西，但佢係九龍返學（佢話佢果間係band 1)，我話又會咁嘅，佢話返我係新界西住但港島返學（我會同買家講住邊同係邊返學，睇吓大家可以點就）都好有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我話咁大專不嬲唔係區區都有，你住果區冇或者你讀果科要出得遠咪要去遠啲讀，跟住我就話中學嘅話我會揀返我果區嘅中學，然後佢打咗個笑喊emo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2:<br />\n呢個就係個中學生，我同佢講我1700放學，行去鐵站都要5-10分鐘，大約1705-1710見，佢1645就到咗，原本都話可以等，之後係1655開始係咁係wts chur我問我完未到未直到見到佢，佢話佢1710後一定要走，因為有另一單交收<br />\n<br />\n3:<br />\n呢個就唔知中定小學生，極耐覆機、成日就唔到時間、好突然咁話邊日咩時間得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經無視咗佢<br />\n<br />\n4:<br />\n跟住有個小學生嚟，同第3個差唔多，佢係ig有利申唔可以秒覆同埋出街有時間限制，原本有係咁問佢幾時得，之後都廢事理佢"},{"pid":"b7372d351cf6f72e87fa3d2635559c506ec25b5f","tid":406160,"uid":82917,"like":8,"dislike":33,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:13:07.000Z","msg":"上網買野=on9<br />\n你仲世界級打篇野屌鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7a1c9de2079252345741fdbb1d951a15e5ec3a","tid":406160,"uid":88343,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上網買野=on9<br />\n你仲世界級打篇野屌鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買野有唔同方式，網上買係其中一個，有乜好on9?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吓吓出去買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4603bd0dc94bc557abdebbe5bdde998f1d5d9c66","tid":406160,"uid":135197,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:16:46.000Z","msg":"第1個我覺得情有可原嘅<br />\nband1學校有得讀唔同區都唔會say no"},{"pid":"31ed4530f042450aa86d622166b1c02044fd9ef6","tid":406160,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"中 小學生係咁架啦 ，番學時間唔得<br />\n遲d 番又問長問短 又想格下價 拖你耐d"},{"pid":"35747bcf754de05bee1036f612a289ccbf0c585f","tid":406160,"uid":138102,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"跨區返學有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441e72b6ca6fba2908c708d8b0ddbea20914078c","tid":406160,"uid":88343,"like":2,"dislike":76,"score":-74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跨區返學有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇話唔得，我覺得中學會少見啲姐，當我見識少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b5c1b6225256c7c30bec7d1b4a40cb8ab9846c","tid":406160,"uid":3932,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"10蚊都要R平啲"},{"pid":"1d59012ababf48f1c92d9b0ca2db124555223841","tid":406160,"uid":17578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跨區返學有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇話唔得，我覺得中學會少見啲姐，當我見識少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我中學屯門返旺角呀 見到未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44006d0a707703ef0ad5d92039f71246bddeaf7","tid":406160,"uid":88343,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"<bloc