if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549b691bd0e5510b6c1b05c55bd4705f33c14266","tid":406160,"uid":88343,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主on9到爆<br />\n我屌你老母屌死你全家呀</blockquote><br />\n唔好咁話自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好行唔送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033a2859962659fb9a038fe26bcefbd596ccc24e","tid":406160,"uid":88343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔比人搬左屋咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前有同學係將軍澳搬去新界北<br />\n都係日日返將軍澳返學<br />\n人地私人事都要打出黎做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  關你撚事 咁都叫世界級</blockquote><br />\n我好奇人地會咁姐，又唔係話一定要係自己果區讀<br />\n宜家變做係咁屌我點解唔比跨境返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得世界級係因為唔止得一單"},{"pid":"9f10922dee1e6c093b2faa50a32ff93e38e5b542","tid":406160,"uid":88343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地跨區返學關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我遇過個中學生<br />\n交收俾勁多硬幣我 都算啦<br />\n我就當面數俾佢睇下啦<br />\n差左15蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾埋戶口佢 催左佢幾次都話唔得<br />\n一時又話要去婆婆度<br />\n一時又話咩朋友入左醫院<br />\n一時又話唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算鬼數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉，遇著呢啲真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f32fff09a6328ddd0b68e0ecbf7746f93deb6d","tid":406160,"uid":97863,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"原來唔凈止得我一個覺得樓主語癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2e34b2d6bd2df997f4b15134631d8acb985892","tid":406160,"uid":135197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第1個我覺得情有可原嘅<br />\nband1學校有得讀唔同區都唔會say no</blockquote><br />\n普通小區band 1都要跨區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話皇仁、喇叭同陳庭佳之類全港性band 1就話跨區都要去啫</blockquote><br />\n九龍都有傳統名校嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔排除係地區"},{"pid":"8b1814087d28f86572aa43d3930d43df3e89f831","tid":406160,"uid":88343,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚野當你見識少<br />\n擺到明係你井底之蛙<br />\n自己未撚見過=無<br />\nGoodest logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇話冇見過喎，見得少姐，我知會有跨區返學<br />\n連登仔真係好鍾意話人未見話過=覺得冇，好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0326ebda1a5310dcca8e7c29c2bd28c0ed77d89d","tid":406160,"uid":97863,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"其實網上買嘢都唔知佢係出嚟做嘢定讀緊書～<br />\n<br />\n但遇到個d一開波話自己係學生哥嗰啲我就一定唔會減價，仲一定要過嚟我嗰區交收（其實時下d學生哥有的是錢同時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），<strong>。</strong>咁如果撞著d打工仔就一定互相就就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上係放嘢心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad37b3177d0cf82605af8f5011d7e2f434564dd","tid":406160,"uid":31572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:08:34.000Z","msg":"樓主啲中文要進修下<br />\n睇到我黑人問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e60114973b162bb5c5653603877d3ed1820617","tid":406160,"uid":79463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:10:37.000Z","msg":"其實我做賣家 有時就唔到時間 同區都會寄順豐.... 多客上黎就唔計個十幾蚊架啦..."},{"pid":"50e250028fff2abd5393c696d