/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來可以咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝建議，遲吓都試吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721e27b06593f911141a01487d67f118736c38d1","tid":406160,"uid":88343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我做賣家 有時就唔到時間 同區都會寄順豐.... 多客上黎就唔計個十幾蚊架啦...</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲吓可能都試吓嘅"}]}